This bag is made with an unbelievably clean dead-stock fabric which dates from the early 1900's, possible the late 1800's.  The graduating colours within the stripes themselves are indicative of the date of the fabric.  
It is very rare to find this fabric in such good, un-used condition.

Very Limited Edition.

name: Leather Care
description:
Fiebings 4 Way leather conditioner is perfect for use on our soft and hard leathers.

Use a soft cloth to apply the conditioner over the leather and allow to sink in and dry completely.

Don't panic when it darkens the leather as you apply.  It will dry to the colour it was before, but better conditioned!

Buff with another clean soft cloth.

Perfect for scratches and general care.
